          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Gas-out irradiations were done with Al and Fe foils",
                " to establish correction factors for neutron back-",
                " ground using 27Al(n,p)27Mg, 27Al(n,alpha)24Na and",
                " 55Fe(n,p)55Mn reactions.",
                ".Corrections were made also for",
                " -Neutron flux fluctuations during irradiations",
                " -Coincidence losses, gamma-ray abundance",
                " -Gamma-ray self-absorption",
                " -Detector efficiency",
                " -Radial dependence of detector efficiency",
                " -Difference between the geometries of sample and",
                "  calibration sources",
                " -Yield of chemical separation sources"
              ]
            }
          ],
